---
title: <small>ACM/IRTF</small><br> Applied Networking Research Workshop
logo_hidden: true
---

- loc = @item.path =~ /^\/[^\/]*$/ ? '' : @item.path.gsub(/\w+\.\w+$/, '').gsub(/[^\/\.]+/, "..").gsub(/^\//, '')

%p.text-center
  %img.img-fluid.center-block{ src: relative_path_to("/img/anrp_logo.png") }

%p.lead
  The ACM, IRTF &amp; ISOC Applied Networking Research Workshops (ANRW) provide a
  forum for researchers, vendors, network operators and the Internet standards
  community to present and discuss emerging results in applied networking
  research.

%p
  In order to foster this cross-community collaboration, the workshops will be
  co-located with IETF standards meetings once a year (typically in July), and
  will be organized in a way that allows ample time for discussion and interaction,
  and not just paper presentations.

%div.row.mt-4
  - @items.find_all(%r{./(\d+)/index.*}).sort_by{ |item| item[:order] }.each do |item|
    %div.card.col-xs-6.col-sm-4.col-md-3.col-lg-3
      %div.card-body
        %a{ href: item.path }
          %img.img-fluid{ src: "#{item.path.split("/")[-1]}/photo.jpg", alt: "ANRP Location" }
        %h3.text-center
          %a.link-underline-light{ href: item.path } #{item[:menu]}
        %p.card-text.text-center
          #{item[:location].to_s}
          %br
          #{item[:date].to_s}

%div.row.mt-4
  %div.col-lg-6
    = render '/anrw/2024/sc_.*', blurb: true
  %div.col-lg-6
    %h2 Sponsors
    = render '/anrw/sponsors_.*'
    %br

    %h2 Organisation
    %p
      %a{ :href => "/anrw/planning/"} 
        Notes for ANRW Organisers

